E5%8A%A1%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%B1%80">@未来事务管理局</a>，共同发起「<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B%E5%A4%A7%E7%88%86%E7%82%B82022%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B%E5%A4%A7%E7%88%86%E7%82%B82022%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#故事大爆炸2022#</span></a>」征文大赛。<br>如果你爱写作，如果你有好故事，这将是属于你的时刻！<br>报名详情：<a href="https://weibo.cn/sinaurl?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpr.wufazhuce.com%2Fzw2022%2F" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a><br><br>打破故事的界限，逾越虚构与真实、文字与影像的鸿沟，「<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B%E5%A4%A7%E7%88%86%E7%82%B82022%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B%E5%A4%A7%E7%88%86%E7%82%B82022%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#故事大爆炸2022#</span></a>」致力于为中国文化影视市场寻找久违的真正好故事。无论你是非虚构作者或科幻达人、无论你写热血青春或悬疑奇案，这里都将是你的舞台。本次大赛选题广阔，鼓励多类型文字创作，为甄选出的优质故事配备出版、影视资源，探索故事的多种样貌，打造书影一体的文学体验。<br><br>转发此条微博并圈出一位你身边热爱写作的朋友，抽6人各送300元写作基金，9月1日（大赛截稿日）开。<br><br>同时也感谢本次大赛的合作方们，我们故事里见！<br><a href="https://weibo.com/n/%E4%B8%AD%E5%BD%B1%E8%82%A1%E4%BB%BD">@中影股份</a><br><a href="https://weibo.com/n/%E7%8C%AB%E7%9C%BC%E5%BD%B1%E8%A7%86">@猫眼影视</a><br><a href="https://weibo.com/n/%E5%A3%B9%E5%90%8C%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C">@壹同制作</a><br><a href="https://weibo.com/n/%E4%B8%87%E5%90%88%E5%A4%A9%E5%AE%9C">@万合天宜</a><br><a href="https://weibo.com/n/%E4%BA%BA%E9%A9%AC%E5%88%B6%E9%80%A0">@人马制造</a><br><a href="https://weibo.com/n/%E6%81%92%E4%B8%9A%E5%BD%B1%E4%B8%9A">@恒业影业</a><img style="" src="https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/001Vyw6Xly1h47oumurxej60u05w9dty02.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img class="rss_img" src="">]]></description><link>https://weibo.com/1766610575/LCwPLicCy</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://weibo.com/1766610575/LCwPLicCy</guid><pubDate>2022-07-16 18:50:06</pubDate></item><item